api_list.name: Updated Documents
api_list.description: Search documents that have been updated after a certain date or within a date interval

optional_parameters.name: t
optional_parameters.description:
Document type, one of:  
pil (Patient Information Leaflet), spc (Summary of Product Characteristics), par (Public Assessment Report), sds (Safety Data Sheet), man (User Manual), inf (Product Information), mmr (Additional Risk Minimisation Measures), hta (Health Technology Assessment Report)

optional_parameters.name: c
optional_parameters.description: See the Supported countries section in the Developers Manual

optional_parameters.name: f
optional_parameters.description: Field optional parameter, if present it can only have 1 value. Perform date comparison on this attribute (date when record was updated in the myHealthbox database) instead of the default one (date when the actual document was updated).

optional_parameters.name: l
optional_parameters.description: See the Supported countries section in the Developers Manual.
